Date:   Thu Oct 4 17:03:13 2018 +0200

    python: extend core classes with __str__
    
    This way print() and str() yield the XML representation of an object:
    
      \#include gyoto.core as gy
      sc=gy.Scenery()
      print(sc)
      string=str(sc)
      print(string)

